value.string: To purge the articles/items from the particular policy number if classname,Itemname and Itemvalue in the input excel file matches with the horison values.
1. Looping all the class names in horison and compare with the clasname given in the input file. if macthes click on the particular classname to go into item description page.
2.In item description page looping all the itemnames and their corresponding itemvalues  in horison and compare with the itemname and itemvalue given in the input file. if macthes purge it.
